Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.74,0:29:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来像密码\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They look like... codes?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.44,0:29:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是坐标\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe coordinates?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.79,0:29:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你认为这是他们藏人的地点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So you think this is about where they're hiding people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.29,0:29:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为什么不写这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why don't we write about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.20,0:29:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.56,0:29:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要证据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.69,0:30:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这么重大  这么爆炸性的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Something this big, this explosive?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.80,0:30:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要破解密码\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We -- We need a key to crack the code.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.23,0:30:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}U-Until we have that,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.30,0:30:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我会先写塞巴斯蒂安的盗窃行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll write about Sebastian's heist...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.71,0:30:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,勒住帕梅拉的脖子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and hang it around Pamela's neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.61,0:30:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,当人们发现她不站在自己这边时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean, when everyone finds out that she's not on their side,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.98,0:30:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会质疑关于这里的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they're gonna question everything about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.40,0:30:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,然后会出现以前提到的起义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hence the aforementioned uprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.06,0:30:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不  没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, hey, hey, hey! It's -- It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.18,0:30:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们需要帮助  所以我叫他来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought we could use help, so I told him to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.12,0:30:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我迟到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.36,0:30:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我在为这件事拉更多盟友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Trying to round up a few more for the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.19,0:30:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-天啊  -我告诉他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Geez. - I told him
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.10,0:30:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要更多人手  帮我们发文章\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we'd needed more people to get the article out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.26,0:30:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一整个关系网  愿意在黎明时分动手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I got a whole network, ready and willing to ride at dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.89,0:30:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们真要这样做吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.42,0:31:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,动手吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.25,0:34:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我等这一刻很久了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have waited for this moment for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.18,0:34:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你想要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.47,0:34:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很久以来  我自己也想要这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wanted it myself for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.07,0:34:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会杀我  那对我来说太轻松了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can't kill me. That would be too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.42,0:34:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想杀我  你早就下手了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If that was what you wanted, you would've done it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.93,0:34:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要我受折磨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You want me to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.18,0:34:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,感受到你所感受的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Feel everything that you felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.05,0:34:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.52,0:34:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你在心里觉得  这能减轻你的痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}'Cause somewhere inside you, you think that'll take away your pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.99,0:34:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,减轻不了的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.80,0:35:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.42,0:35:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.11,0:35:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,等我做完之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By the time I'm done...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.40,0:35:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你所爱的人都会死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everyone you love will be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.78,0:35:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜这样就扯平了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then I guess that makes us even.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.27,0:35:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我夺走你的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I took your family,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.28,0:35:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你夺走我的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you take mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.70,0:35:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,因果报应  自有天意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nature has a way of taking care of these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.46,0:35:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是天意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.21,0:35:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,或命运\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.01,0:36:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.28,0:36:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我杀了你的人  因为这是我想要的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I killed your people because it was what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.39,0:36:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这是你想要的  莉娅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If this is what you want, Leah...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.81,0:36:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那就动手吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.43,0:36:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要  那就动手吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You want it, so do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.64,0:36:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,快啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.89,0:37:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在里面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.05,0:38:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,长官  你没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.87,0:38:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,别管了  去另一边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let it go! On the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.20,0:38:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来支援我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who's my backup here?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.52,0:38:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,停火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hold your fire!
